<isis lang="en">
    <stitle>RADIATOR SHUTTERS - TROUBLESHOOTING</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcsubsec>
        <title>TROUBLESHOOTING</title>
        <svcsubsecinfo>
            <specpara>
                <note>
                    <para>Adjust the shutter thermostat to open the shutters when the engine outlet coolant is 10&#176;F.
                        (6&#176;C.) above the engine thermostat opening temperature. For a 170&#176;F. (77&#176;C.)
                        engine thermostat, the shutters should start to open when the engine outlet temperature is 180&#176;F.
                        (82&#176;C.). The shutters should be fully open when the outlet coolant temperature reaches 190&#176;F.
                        (88&#176;C.).
                    </para>
                </note>
            </specpara>
        </svcsubsecinfo>
        <svcproc svcproctype="troubleshoot" graphiccount="0">
            <title>TROUBLESHOOTING CHART</title>
            <table id="hl1200501">
                <title>Troubleshooting Chart</title>
                <tgroup cols="3">
                    <colspec colname="1" colwidth="1.97in"/>
                    <colspec colname="2" colwidth="2.08in"/>
                    <colspec colname="3" colwidth="2.01in"/>
                    <thead>
                        <row rowsep="0">
                            <entry colname="1">
                                <para>Condition</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry colname="2">
                                <para>Possible Cause</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry colname="3">
                                <para>Possible Remedy</para>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody>
                        <row rowsep="0">
                            <entry colname="1">
                                <para>Engine overheating</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry colname="2">
                                <para>Shutter vanes do not open</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry colname="3">
                                <para>Refer to ELECTRICAL TROUBLE- SHOOTING SECTION for your vehicle.</para>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row rowsep="0">
                            <entry colname="1">
                                <para>Shutter vanes remain closed at the upper temperature limit</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry colname="2">
                                <para>Ignition wires reversed from positive to negative terminal on the thermal sensing
                                    switch
                                </para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry colname="3">
                                <para>Turn the sensing switch the correct way.</para>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row rowsep="0">
                            <entry colname="1">
                                <para></para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry colname="2">
                                <para>Faulty thermal sensing switch</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry colname="3">
                                <para>Replace the sensing switch; refer to ELECTRICAL TROUBLE- SHOOTING SECTION for your
                                    vehicle.
                                </para>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row rowsep="0">
                            <entry colname="1">
                                <para></para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry colname="2">
                                <para>Defective cylinder</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry colname="3">
                                <para>Replace the cylinder.</para>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                    </tbody>
                </tgroup>
            </table>
        </svcproc>
